</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>吉利夥拍 Waymo   美國建立自動駕駛的士車隊</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/01/geely-waymo-autonomous-taxi-fleet/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=geely-waymo-autonomous-taxi-fleet</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 31 Dec 2021 22:51:35 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[geely]]></category><category><![CDATA[Waymo]]></category><category><![CDATA[Zeekr]]></category><category><![CDATA[吉利]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078839</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>中國汽車集團吉利（Geely）本週二宣佈，旗下的豪華電動車品牌 Zeekr 將會與 Alphabet 子公司，主力研發自動駕駛技術的 Waymo 合作，攜手於美國建立全電動的自動駕駛的士車隊，並在當地提供 Waymo One 電召客車服務。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>中國汽車集團吉利（Geely）本週二宣佈，旗下的豪華電動車品牌 Zeekr 將會與 Alphabet 子公司，主力研發自動駕駛技術的 Waymo 合作，攜手於美國建立全電動的自動駕駛的士車隊，並在當地提供 Waymo One 電召客車服務。</p><p><span id="more-1078839"></span></p><p>吉利和 Waymo 在新聞稿中表示，車隊所用的電動車將會由 Zeekr，於他們位處瑞典哥德堡的基地設計和開發，並且採用一種新的專屬和開源流動架構。當新車運到美國並交付 Waymo，就會在車上安裝稱為 Waymo Driver 的自動駕駛技術。</p><p>兩家公司均沒有提到配備 Waymo Driver 的 Zeekr 電動車何時會投入服務，唯一確定是這些電動車未來會加入 Waymo One 車隊。Google 在 2009 年開始開發自動駕駛汽車，及後改名 Waymo 並分拆成為 Alphabet 子公司，Waymo 的自動駕駛客貨車在亞利桑那鳳凰城已經測試了超過 1 年，但還未有全自動駕駛技術正式推出的時間表。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2021/12/29/geelys-zeekr-partners-with-waymo-to-build-its-self-driving-taxi-fleet-for-the-us-market/">gizmochina</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=72T9B_0uX6I:kmbOsTYsEYg:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=72T9B_0uX6I:kmbOsTYsEYg:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【評測】Canon RF 無反行山鏡頭孖寶 16mm 2.8 廣角小痰罐 + 100-400mm 平民長焦距，人像+風景實拍</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/31/canon-rf-double-kit/dc/dc-test/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=canon-rf-double-kit</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 31 Dec 2021 10:55:36 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[相機測試]]></category><category><![CDATA[評測]]></category><category><![CDATA[canon]]></category><category><![CDATA[RF]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078773</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Canon RF 鏡頭除了專業級型號陸續補完之外，一般消費級鏡頭都愈出愈多。最近 Canon 就推出兩支價格非 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Canon RF 鏡頭除了專業級型號陸續補完之外，一般消費級鏡頭都愈出愈多。最近 Canon 就推出兩支價格非常親民的 RF 鏡頭，分別為超廣角定焦鏡頭 Canon RF 16mm f/2.8 STM，以及平民版長焦距鏡頭 Canon RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM，非常適合行山、旅遊，或者一般消閒攝影用途，例如你已經有一支大光圈標準鏡頭，想輔以較廉價的廣角、長焦距鏡頭來補完手上的焦段，今次介紹的兩支鏡頭都十分合適。兩支鏡頭的官方建議零售價分別只是$2,680（廣角定焦）以及$5,780（長焦距），都是一般玩家都負擔得起。小編就同 unwire 記者小嫺一齊試試這兩支新鏡，看看在價格相宜之外，質素是否能夠令人滿意。</p><h2>RF 行山孖寶：一支超廣角定焦、一支長焦距</h2><p>首先分享這兩支鏡頭拿上手的手感。這支 RF 16mm f/2.8 STM（下稱 RF 16 2.8STM）鏡身高約 40.2mm，闊度約 69.2mm，同師兄 50 STM 的體積差不多一樣，是極為經典的「小痰罐」黃金 size，且重量只有 165g，如果你去行山、旅遊主要用標準鏡影相，輔以超廣角鏡完成你的拍攝之旅，本鏡就非常合適。你可把它長期放在相機袋內「看門口」，必要時才拿出來使用。小編在出門時把 EOS R5 與此鏡掛在頸上便出門，整天也不會感到重量壓力，想輕便的朋友，配合 R6 或 RP 機身更佳。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0019-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078984" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0019-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0019-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0019-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0019-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0013-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078983" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0013-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0013-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0013-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0013-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0006-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078982" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0006-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0006-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0006-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0006-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0013-2.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>長焦鏡 RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM（下稱 RF 100-400 f/5.6-8）同樣輕便攜帶，其體積就有如一支礦泉水，重量只有 635g，對於一支涵蓋 400mm 焦距的鏡頭來說是相當輕便，長期手持拍攝也不會感到壓力。鏡身已有 AF/MF 切換與防手震功能開關，操作方便。裝上機後，機鏡的重量平衡也相當不錯，沒有鏡身過重的問題。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0020-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078985" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0020-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0020-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0020-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0020-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0008-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0008-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0008-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0008-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0008-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0012-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0012-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0012-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0012-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0012-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0009-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0009-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0009-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0009-6-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0009-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲在 400mm 焦段會再伸長一點</p><h2>RF 16mm f/2.8 STM 實用性評測</h2><h2>極輕盈超廣角定焦鏡，原廠鏡少見</h2><p>市面上各大廠的廣角鏡頭，一般都是高階型號、大光圈，確是又大又重又貴，很難吸引到入門用家購買，更難隨時拿出街用。這支 RF 16 2.8STM 其實都有 f/2.8 光圈，日間拍攝足夠有餘，而在晚間拍攝夜景，f/2.8 光圈都足夠。特別是現在 EOS R5、R6 的可用 ISO 感光度已去到 12800（小編個人意見），基本上就算是夜景，手持拍攝也可去到 1/15 左右的快門，配合主機防手震系統，可說是遊刃有餘，用戶毋須擔心一定要落腳架才可影到靚相。而在白天攝影，這支「小痰罐」可給你解像力不錯的相片，從相片中央至到邊緣，線條都頗為實淨。</p><p><a title="0G8A2905_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787103786/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787103786_3e2a22c88b_b.jpg" alt="0G8A2905_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/8, 1/400, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3169_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787982685/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787982685_24bb5b0ff9_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3169_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/5.6, 1/1000, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3094_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787358738/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787358738_d799a9420f_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3094_R" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/5.6, 1/1250, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A2929_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787354433/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787354433_910993f756_b.jpg" alt="0G8A2929_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/10, 1/400, ISO 100</p><p>廣角鏡頭除了拍攝開揚風景之外，都可用來近拍，營造誇張的透視感覺。RF 16 2.8STM 就提供了 0.26x 放大率，最近拍攝距離可近至 0.13 米，用戶可拍攝小物件或超近攝時，背景產生強烈的透視感，而 f/2.8 大光圈也為你帶來焦外的散景。</p><p><a title="0G8A2945_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787990220/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787990220_dd08069681_b.jpg" alt="0G8A2945_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/8, 1/80, ISO 320</p><p><a title="0G8A2914_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787726319/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787726319_1529f5f27a_b.jpg" alt="0G8A2914_R" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/8, 1/125, ISO 100</p><h2>防眩光、鬼影效果良好</h2><p>鏡頭價格雖平，但鏡身內置包含超光譜塗膜的鏡片，大大減低了鬼影現象，也加強了防眩光的表現。對著太陽直射都很容易獲得滿意相片，而在 f/22 時的星芒效果也令人滿意。</p><p><a title="0G8A2849_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787103411/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787103411_6b65c2f77e_b.jpg" alt="0G8A2849_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/18, 1/100, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A2966_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787979950/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787979950_ea9bbc2195_b.jpg" alt="0G8A2966_R" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/22, 1/200, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3174_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787997135/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787997135_742df91560_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3174_R" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/22, 1/250, ISO 100</p><h2>放入 Lightroom 執一執效果更佳</h2><p>而作為便攜中階鏡頭，四個角落的變暗問題較為嚴重。如果你對於相片有較高要求的話，建議把 RAW 相片放到 Photoshop 的 Camera RAW 等進行後期修正。最近 Adobe 已經推出了相關 profile，用家只要更新 Camera RAW 便可。自動修正毋須用家操心，一放入去便會自己搞妥。在處理過後，四角暗角問題，以及變形都會得到大幅輕減。</p><p><a title="0G8A3210_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51786292807/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51786292807_6e22ffb2f4_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3210_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/3.5, 1/10, ISO 400</p><p><a title="0G8A3169_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787982685/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787982685_24bb5b0ff9_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3169_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 16mm f/2.8 STM @16mm, f/5.6, 1/1000, ISO 100</p><h2>RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM 實用性評測</h2><h2>中級鏡對焦速度、準確度仍十分強</h2><p>今次介紹的 RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM 作為長焦鏡來說其重量可說是相當輕盈。較長時間拍攝，也不怕手部疲倦。好多人都擔心本鏡光圈只有 f/5.6-8，在 400mm 時拍攝比較困難。不過小編在實際拍攝夜景，配合 EOS R5 相機拍攝遠景，發現其對焦性能頗為強勁。今次小編從港島西環對開沿岸，向青衣、汀九方面拍攝，即使用上 400mm 焦段，如果對準的影像為有光照射的物件，其對焦速度頗為快速，而且拍到得來的相片也能印證到頗高的對焦準確度，這給予小編很大的驚喜。</p><p><a title="0G8A2819_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787345543/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787345543_9b55291721_b.jpg" alt="0G8A2819_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @100mm, f/5.6, 1/500, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3120_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51784647551/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51784647551_17521d0c0f_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3120_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @400mm, f/8.0, 1/640, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3067_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51784876293/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51784876293_81a1eb897f_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3067_R" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @300mm, f/8.0, 1/400, ISO 12800</p><p><a title="0G8A3315_R2_1" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51785285714/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51785285714_d935d44c2a_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3315_R2_1" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲西環岸邊在夜晚清晰捕捉到青衣對開開面快速船隻 Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @400mm, f/8.0, 1/30, ISO 51200,  RAW 檔案原圖經 Adobe Camera RAW 調整雜訊減少+10, 雜色減少+60</p><h2>6 級防手震令 400mm 焦距、1/15 秒快門可常用拍夜景</h2><p>而且鏡身已內置有 IS 防手震系統，可提供達 5.5 級鏡身防手震效果，如配合 EOS R5 或 R6 使用，配合機身防手震系統，防手震效能更可達 6 級。小編把 ISO 感光度提升至 16000，在拍攝有光照明的夜景時快門可得到 1/15，配合 6 級防手震效果，即使在 400mm 焦距時，可輕鬆拍到清晰度頗為滿意的相片。</p><p><a title="0G8A3255_R2" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51785226679/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51785226679_c5fd59e44b_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3255_R2" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @400mm, f/8.0, 1/15, ISO 16000,  RAW 檔案原圖經 Adobe Camera RAW 調整雜訊減少+10, 雜色減少+40, <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51783775732/in/photostream/">原圖</a></p><h2>影花影蝴蝶同樣就手</h2><p>本鏡還有一個強項，就是其 0.41 最高放大倍率。在 400mm 焦距時，最近對焦距離可以近至只有 1.05 米，即差不多等如變了做半支「Marco 鏡」，拍攝花朵、蝴蝶都好輕鬆 easy，旅遊攝影可更為得心應手。</p><p><a title="0G8A2934_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51784878748/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51784878748_4b40169d66_b.jpg" alt="0G8A2934_R" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @400mm, f/10, 1/500, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3140_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51784900058/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51784900058_bf3620034d_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3140_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲行山經常見到的芒草，背景是反射的海面，Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @400mm, f/80, 1/640, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3161_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51784648966/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51784648966_ae62017ddb_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3161_R" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @100mm, f/5.6, 1/640, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3041_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51785259739/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51785259739_4a4350bfe8_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3041_R" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @300mm, f/8, 1/400, ISO 250</p><h2>整體清晰度中規中矩</h2><p>用家也要留意放大 100% 後聞相的表現，小編認為在 100mm 至到 400mm，都維持到中規中矩的解像力，在 EOS R5 相機 4500 萬像素的加持下，除非你需要打印很大的海報，不然也可放 Facebook 等社交網絡，以至 Flickr 分享也是可接受的，對於售價在數千元擁有 100mm 至到 400mm 變焦幅度的鏡頭來說已屬不錯。</p><p><a title="0G8A2815_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51787966515/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51787966515_aa7d0e2455_b.jpg" alt="0G8A2815_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @174mm, f/7.1, 1/400, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3013_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51784887303/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51784887303_dc285b75f0_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3013_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @400mm, f/11, 1/250, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3014_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51785259064/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51785259064_df39d2dfc3_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3014_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @400mm, f/8, 1/400, ISO 100</p><p><a title="0G8A3124_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51783822882/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51783822882_61606b5da7_b.jpg" alt="0G8A3124_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @400mm, f/8, 1/400, ISO 160（手持攝影）</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0G8A3124_R 副本.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1078796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/0G8A3124_R 副本.jpg" alt="" width="690" height="400" /></a>▲100％放大</p><p><a title="0G8A2992_R" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/51785506680/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/51785506680_563c73d727_b.jpg" alt="0G8A2992_R" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>▲Canon EOS R5, RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM @118mm, f/6.3, 1/400, ISO 100</p><h2>總結：RF 抵玩實用入門鏡<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span>行山影風景最實用</h2><p>如果你已經有一支不錯的 24-70mm 常用焦段鏡頭，投放於廣角鏡、遠攝鏡的資金有限，今次 Canon 新推的兩支入門鏡就可積極考慮。小編特別喜歡 RF 16mm f/2.8 STM，它鏡身輕盈、價格相宜，在其他相機品牌實屬少見，Canon 用戶可買定「看門口」，隨時拿出來使用。它非常適合行山旅遊，間中想拍幾張超廣角相片的朋友使用，隨時為你省回廣角變焦鏡的錢（如果你是拍攝廣角相片為主，當然可考慮入手更貴的鏡頭）。</p><p>至於 RF 100-400mm f/5.6-8 IS USM 雖然解像力對比貴鏡頭會稍遜一點，不過它配合 EOS R5、R6 有著穩定的防手震能力、令人滿意的對焦效能，再加上輕盈的鏡身，與相宜價格，給 RF 接環用戶一個不錯的選擇。鏡頭重量同樣適合行山旅遊之用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0003-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078989" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0003-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0003-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0003-6-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unwire0003-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
